reviewText: False advertising two hot girls on the cover and you think your gonna get to see them like the description says and there not even in the movie this DVD is a total rip off from Amazon to make them 20 bucks!

Sorry to say this is not what you think it is. Went straight into garbage. Firs few minutes are one thing, 40 more mintues are completely different than cover. "You can't judge a book by its cover" was never so true.
